# Code ownership for Skeldir API Contracts repository
#
# This file defines who must review changes to specific paths.
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Contract ownership - backend team leads must review all contract changes
api-contracts/ @backend-team-leads

# CI/CD workflows - backend team leads own CI configuration
.github/workflows/contract-validation.yml @backend-team-leads
.github/workflows/contract-publish.yml @backend-team-leads

# Breaking changes require frontend lead review for SDK/FE alignment
# Note: Breaking changes are detected via CI, but FE lead should be notified
api-contracts/openapi/v1/**/*.yaml @frontend-lead

# Repository configuration files
README.md @backend-team-leads
